    "description": "自由选择机甲，调整装备，构筑你的完美牌组。走进这款类Rogue冒险游戏，尝试各种卡牌，寻找强大的卡牌组合，尽情感受战术作战的激烈和牌组构筑的巧妙！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自由选择机甲装备</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1288540/extras/4fe5bcd218e15ad5e9ba8539bba03b9e.poster.avif?t=1768204031\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1288540/extras/4fe5bcd218e15ad5e9ba8539bba03b9e.webm?t=1768204031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1288540/extras/4fe5bcd218e15ad5e9ba8539bba03b9e.mp4?t=1768204031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>自由选择你的机甲骨架，毕竟每个驾驶员的战斗思路各不相同，有人青睐便于近战的攻击骨架，有人选择潜行狙击骨架，有人则偏好纯粹的激光火力。游戏期间，安装新的装备，令机甲骨架升级成为新的型号，即可增强骨架的相关性能。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >构筑你的完美牌组</h2>消灭你的对手，即可获得武器和护盾等各类装备。胜利能够令你的机甲得到新的“玩具”，改换这些“玩具”就会改变你的作战牌组。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >走上战场，测试机甲的战斗实力</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1288540/extras/290c61413b531608373a82a8c9354c75.poster.avif?t=1768204031\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1288540/extras/290c61413b531608373a82a8c9354c75.webm?t=1768204031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1288540/extras/290c61413b531608373a82a8c9354c75.mp4?t=1768204031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>无数武器和物品等你发现与尝试——激光、机关枪、等离子步枪、狙击炮、刀剑、大锤、无人机、地雷、力场、喷气发动机以及其他更为特别的武器和物品，例如火箭手甲、鞭子、镰刀、斗篷、冲剂锥和迷你核弹！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >尽情感受战术作战的激烈</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1288540/extras/87508e0ab710ef1dbf16a7d469bbbd54.poster.avif?t=1768204031\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1288540/extras/87508e0ab710ef1dbf16a7d469bbbd54.webm?t=1768204031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1288540/extras/87508e0ab710ef1dbf16a7d469bbbd54.mp4?t=1768204031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>预先判断对手的行动，根据战况临机应变，及时调整作战策略，包抄、突击、埋伏、掩体躲避抑或精准打击敌方的致命要害。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >寻找强大的卡牌组合</h2>探索独一无二的卡牌组合，压制敌人，占得上风；或者探索超强组合，一回合战胜敌方头目或者无伤战胜敌人。选择最高的难度，测试你的卡牌组合。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >尽力保护机甲的身体部件</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1288540/extras/31531a6f2f847843c743a82517d1681d.poster.avif?t=1768204031\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1288540/extras/31531a6f2f847843c743a82517d1681d.webm?t=1768204031\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1288540/extras/31531a6f2f847843c743a82517d1681d.mp4?t=1768204031\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>机甲的每个身体部件都有各自的护甲和寿命，务必平衡各个装备的性能关系，确保牌组时刻能够充分发挥作用，从而充分保证机甲自身的身体部件。部件一旦毁坏，相关卡牌就打不出去了！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的前路由你自己决定</h2>谨慎选择自己前进的方向，或战或避，根据自身当前的装备配置决定。可以为了丰厚的回报，承担巨大的风险，也可以仅仅达成自己的目标。各类机械正在遭受异界AI的影响，仔细调查，看看这个AI到底来自何方。",
